This is a lottery ticket blockchain game

Dependencies:
1. nodejs
    - brew install node
2. truffle
    - npm install -g truffle
    - recommended to download Truffle for VS Code extension from
      https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=trufflesuite-csi.truffle-vscode
3. metamask
    - install metamask extension on browser (chrome, firefox, brave, etc.)
    - safari does not have the ability to use extensions
4. Ganache
    - download Ganache from https://trufflesuite.com/ganache/

Running DAPP:
truffle test (tests smart contracts)
truffle compile (compiles smart contracts)
truffle migrate (migrates smart contracts to blockchain)

npm start (launches react in browser)
    - make sure browser has metamask extension installed otherwise you won't be able to use it


Building from scratch:
https://trufflesuite.com/docs/truffle/quickstart/